(179, 1, '2015-05-16 18:40:08', '2015-05-16 18:40:08', '[container customclass="add-top"][row customclass=""][column span="12" customclass="align-center"][page_heading customclass="dark-txt"]Our Team[/page_heading][/column][/row][row customclass=""][column span="12" customclass="align-center"][promo_text customclass="dark-txt"]We consider as a unique kind every member of our team , specialists in their area and always willing to give the 120% to exceed the expectations of our clients.[/promo_text][/column][/row][/container][carousel id="DignityCarousel1" customclass="" fx=""][carousel_item customclass=""][container customclass="add-bottom"][row customclass=""][column span="3" customclass="align-center"][team customclass="" thumb_fx="bounceInDown" panel_fx="bounceInUp" image_url="http://localhost/LieisonWeb/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/team-01.jpg" name="Emerson J. Sanchez" designation="Business Developer" ]It is characterized as a sociable and adaptable mammal, he likes to visit different areas inside and outside the region, capable to communicate in more than one language, he likes to meet new species and establish new long terms relationships\r\n<a href="https://sv.linkedin.com/pub/emerson-sanchez/61/a38/93/es"><img class="aligncenter size-full" src="http://localhost/LieisonWeb/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Iconos-SocialMedia-IN.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" /></a><a href="https://www.facebook.com/javier.barahona.775"><img class="aligncenter size-full" src="http://localhost/LieisonWeb/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Iconos-SocialMedia-FB.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" /></a><a href="https://twitter.com/Javier_stones"><img class="aligncenter size-full" src="http://localhost/LieisonWeb/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Iconos-SocialMedia-TW.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" /></a> [/team][/column][column span="3" customclass="align-center"][team customclass="" thumb_fx="bounceInDown" panel_fx="bounceInUp" image_url="http://localhost/LieisonWeb/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/team-02.jpg" name="Gerson E. Aguirre" designation="Account Manager" ]It is characterized for being a silent and serious kind, he observes, takes mental notes, likes to be organized, to establish and follow procedures when carrying out his activities. Capable to stay at the same place for long periods of time. He loves cantonese fried rice.\r\n<a href="https://sv.linkedin.com/in/geabenitez"><img class="aligncenter size-full" src="http://localhost/LieisonWeb/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Iconos-SocialMedia-IN.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" /></a><a href="https://www.facebook.com/Exeffect"><img class="aligncenter size-full" src="http://localhost/LieisonWeb/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Iconos-SocialMedia-FB.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" /></a><a href="https://twitter.com/geabenitez"><img class="aligncenter size-full" src="http://localhost/LieisonWeb/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Iconos-SocialMedia-TW.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" /></a> [/team][/column][column span="3" customclass="align-center"][team customclass="" thumb_fx="bounceInDown" panel_fx="bounceInUp" image_url="http://localhost/LieisonWeb/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/team-03.jpg" name="Rolando A. Marroquin" designation="Senior Developer"] Probably the weirdest specie between the fauna, he has his own language to express himself. His transportation is based in two wheels and is very noisy while trying to run away quickly. Rumor has it his feeding is based on coffee and soups.\r\n<a href="https://sv.linkedin.com/pub/rolando-arriaza/a1/87b/283/es"><img class="aligncenter size-full" src="http://localhost/LieisonWeb/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Iconos-SocialMedia-IN.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" /></a><a href="https://www.facebook.com/rolando.a.arriaza"><img class="aligncenter size-full" src="http://localhost/LieisonWeb/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Iconos-SocialMedia-FB.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" /></a><a href="https://twitter.com/rolignu"><img class="aligncenter size-full" src="http://localhost/LieisonWeb/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Iconos-SocialMedia-TW.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" /></a> [/team][/column][column span="3" customclass="align-center"][team customclass="" thumb_fx="bounceInDown" panel_fx="bounceInUp" image_url="http://localhost/LieisonWeb/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/team-04.jpg" name="Maya E.\r\nSiliezar" designation="Senior Designer" ] Certainly the most creative specie, she is characterized by being a really quiet and stressed kind, her biggest fear are designs made in Adobe Photoshop. Capable to break a brand new chair in few seconds. Candies are what she enjoys the most.\r\n<a href="https://sv.linkedin.com/pub/maya-siliézar-flores/a5/743/a0a"><img class="aligncenter size-full" src="http://localhost/LieisonWeb/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Iconos-SocialMedia-IN.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" /></a><a href="https://www.facebook.com/maya.siliezar"><img class="aligncenter size-full" src="http://localhost/LieisonWeb/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Iconos-SocialMedia-FB.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" /></a><a href="https://twitter.com/MayaSiliezar"><img class="aligncenter size-full" src="http://localhost/LieisonWeb/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Iconos-SocialMedia-TW.png" alt="" width="50" height="50" /></a> [/team][/column][/row][/container][/carousel_item][/carousel]', 'Team', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '78-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-16 18:40:08', '2015-05-16 18:40:08', '', 78, 'http://localhost/LieisonWeb/index.php/2015/05/16/78-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
