(182, 1, '2015-05-16 18:55:12', '2015-05-16 18:55:12', '[container customclass="add-top" fx="flipInX"][row customclass=""][column span="12" customclass="align-center"][page_heading customclass=""]Our Services[/page_heading][/column][/row][row customclass=""][column span="12" customclass="align-center"][/column][/row][/container][services id="service1" customclass="" ][service_item id="service-01" item_no="1" span="3" customclass="" fx="slideInLeft" heading="GRAPHIC DESIGN" sub_heading="Editorial | Web | Avertising" icon_url="http://localhost/LieisonWeb/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Iconos-Servicios-01.png"] Rely the design of your brand in the hands of our experts and creatives. We specialize in branding, corporate image, advertising design, editorial design and more. We develop your corporate image beginning from the concept of your brand giving life to your ideas converting them into an identity that is visually transmitted allowing to your clients to be attracted to your brand trough your logotype. That and much more is what we are able to do with our design team. \r\n[button url="#" hover_text="Request quote" customclass=""]Have a project?[/button] [/service_item][service_item id="service-02" item_no="2" span="3" customclass="" fx="slideInLeft" heading="DEVELOPMENT" sub_heading="Web | Applications | Movil" icon_url="http://localhost/LieisonWeb/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Iconos-Servicios-03.png"] Your website is a digital presentation letter, Lieison helps you to impress to your clients with a website visually attractive where you can sell your products or services, our designs includes into the website the ability to adapt to every and each device such as smartphones, tablets, laptops, etc. regardless the screen size. We also can integrate your social networks into it. Your Website, Your Business and our ability to take it to the next level.\r\n[button url="#" hover_text="Request quote" customclass=""]Have a project?[/button] [/service_item][service_item id="service-03" item_no="3" span="3" customclass="" fx="slideInRight" heading="SOCIAL MEDIA OPTIMIZATION" sub_heading="Management | Development | Campaings" icon_url="http://localhost/LieisonWeb/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Iconos-Servicios-02.png"] It is not "simply" a social network, it is an advertising tool that allows your brand to reach new consumers with new behaviours and different culture, where we will appropiately take care of the management of campaigns focusing them in your target market, we will provide you with support in statical analysis of interactions and "customer engagement" regarding your brand which will help you to develop the brand positioning that you need and as a result increase your sales. \r\n[button url="#" hover_text="Request quote" customclass=""]Have a project?[/button] [/service_item][service_item id="service-04" item_no="4" span="3" customclass="" fx="slideInRight" heading="PHOTOGRAPHY" sub_heading="Advertising | Events | Others" icon_url="http://localhost/LieisonWeb/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Iconos-Servicios-04.png"] Photography is not a science, but it is art where each angle, each shot, each movement is inevitably valuable to generate visual impact to the people, it is a good way to advertise your brand and also to keep those special moments that mark our lifes. That is something we know at Lieison and we offer to you our tools and knowledge about natural optical and everything that surround us and can be materialized in digital photography. \r\n[button url="#" hover_text="Request quote" customclass=""]Have a project?[/button] [/service_item][/services]', 'Services', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '60-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-16 18:55:12', '2015-05-16 18:55:12', '', 60, 'http://localhost/LieisonWeb/index.php/2015/05/16/60-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
